gymagent: Agents for Gym
=======================

This package provides agents for `openai/gym`.

Lists of agents:
- `AcrobotV1Agent`
- `BipedalWalkerV3Agent`
- `CartPoleV0Agent`
- `LunarlanderV2Agent`, `LunarLanderContinuousV2Agent`
- `MountainCarV0Agent`
- `PendulumV0Agent`
- `PongNoFrameskipAgent`
